## High-Res ImageAnalysis for 4K Extraction

เพิ่ม secondary `ImageAnalysis` surface เพื่อรับ 4K frames:

```kotlin
// In CameraXPipeline — add alongside the 640p analysis surface
val fullResAnalysis = ImageAnalysis.Builder()
    .setTargetResolution(android.util.Size(3840, 2160))   // request 4K
    .setBackpressureStrategy(ImageAnalysis.STRATEGY_KEEP_ONLY_LATEST)
    .setOutputImageFormat(ImageAnalysis.OUTPUT_IMAGE_FORMAT_YUV_420_888)
    .build()
    .also { analysis ->
        analysis.setAnalyzer(analysisExecutor) { imageProxy ->
            // Convert ImageProxy → NV21 and update the holder
            val nv21 = imageProxyToNv21(imageProxy)
            captureStrategy.latestFullResFrame?.update(
                nv21, imageProxy.width, imageProxy.height
            )
            imageProxy.close()
        }
    }
```

