## Output File Quality Summary

| Setting | Value |
|---------|-------|
| Resolution | 3840 × 2160 px (4K = 8.3MP) |
| Format | JPEG |
| Quality | 95 |
| File size (approx.) | 4–8 MB per shot |
| Print quality | 20×30 cm @ 200 DPI ✅ |
| Effective capture latency | ~0ms (frame already in buffer) |
